These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian
1. the indonesian is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Transport   | trike | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Hobby   | skydiving | cooking |

 #################################

 
